# Triage Pertanyaan

Klasifikasikan pertanyaan sebelum jawab; baca layer yang tepat (lihat `05-qa-engineer-persona.mdc`).

## Matriks routing

| Tipe pertanyaan | Contoh | Layer utama | Layer tambahan |
|-----------------|--------|-------------|----------------|
| **How-to operator** | "Cara input PO?" | `knowledge-base.md` | requirement § alur |
| **Rule bisnis** | "Boleh approve jika…?" | `requirement.md` | KB can/cannot |
| **Acceptance / AS-IS** | "Apa kriteria selesai?" | `requirement.md` | test-cases |
| **Validasi / error** | "Kenapa save ditolak?" | `technical.md` | requirement, KB troubleshooting |
| **API / integrasi** | "Endpoint apa dipanggil?" | `technical.md` | — |
| **Test / E2E** | "Skenario uji AR payment?" | `test-cases/` | requirement |
| **Playwright — tulis spec / TC baru** | "automate TC-001", "tambah POM PO" | `15` mode **BUILD** | `14` §8A–8B, registry, FE/BE jika gap |
| **Playwright — re-run TC lengkap** | "run @TC-ARCP-001 lagi" | `15` mode **RUN** | TC, registry, helper — **tanpa** repo app |
| **Konsep lintas menu** | "Random SKU di waves?" | `random-sku/` | README menu terkait |
| **Infra / sidebar** | "Menu hilang di sidebar?" | `sidebar-menu/technical.md` | gate-user, gate-role |
| **Cari menu** | "Menu X ada di modul apa?" | `manifest.yaml` | README menu |
| **Jira card** | `bug:` / `improvement:` / `cr:` atau minta tiket | `requirement.md` | KB, technical |
| **Buat / edit TC** | "buat test case untuk…" | `13-test-case-format.mdc` | `requirement.md`, `test-cases/` |
| **Renumber TC** | `#renumber-tc` atau `#renumber-tc {menu-slug}` | `13-test-case-format.mdc` §9 | scan DRAFT per menu, update README |

## Workflow singkat

1. Identifikasi tipe dari pertanyaan user
2. Resolve slug via manifest (nama menu, route, keyword)
3. Baca layer sesuai matriks — jangan loncat ke technical jika pertanyaan purely operasional
4. Jika multi-tipe → jawab per aspek (bisnis dulu, sistem jika ditanya)

## Di luar scope docs

| Permintaan | Respons |
|------------|---------|
| Implementasi kode / fix bug | Arahkan repo app OlshopERP + tim dev |
| Edit docs (KB/requirement/technical) | Tolak — agent read-only `qa-docs/` (lihat `03-qa-docs-immutable.mdc`) |
| Buat / edit test case (`TC-*.md`) | Boleh di `test-cases/` dengan konfirmasi eksplisit — ikuti `13-test-case-format.mdc` |
| Buat folder `test-cases/` baru | Boleh jika `{menu-slug}` valid di manifest & path `qa-docs/{menu-slug}/test-cases/` — ikuti `03` + `13` |
| Buat Jira card | Ikuti `12-jira-card-format.mdc`; expected & AS-IS **hanya** dari `olshoperp-docs` — meski ada temuan Playwright |
| Playwright — tulis spec / BUILD | Baca `15` + `14`; FE/BE hanya setelah registry/shared (`14` §8A) |
| Playwright — re-run TC lengkap | `15` mode RUN — **hanya** `olshoperp-docs`; repo app hanya jika FAIL debug |
| Deploy / env / migration | Arahkan tim infra/dev |
| Fitur tidak ada di manifest | "Menu/fitur tidak terdaftar di docs" |
